headline: Evercore ISI Lifts PT on AutoZone (AZO) to $4,250 From $4,060
summary: AutoZone, Inc. (NYSE:AZO) is one of the best automotive stocks to buy according to hedge funds. On August 18, Evercore ISI raised the firm’s price target on AutoZone, Inc. (NYSE:AZO) to $4,250 from $4,060 while keeping an Outperform rating on the shares. The firm told investors in a retail earnings preview note that the timing […]
